Dialogs.Dialog: It's okay. Where are we going?
I'm sorry, I have a plan after returning home. Thank you for inviting me.
I see. Well, at least let me send you home.
Well if you want to go...
It's okay, I have time today.
I see, my timing was right.
I'm sorry, I have something to do today. But, if we go home together...
I agree with you. Then, here.
Do you want to go there? Yeah, I don't think so.
I'm sure ▲高嶺＊＊▲ can also enjoy it.
Is it really good? Ok, I understand.
Please hold back. Right now it's a little... I'm sorry.
（... is she in a bad mood?）
I don't want to go home today.
Ok, then lets take a detour.
There are days like that. I'm sorry.
Don't apologize. Let's go home together.
Oh, sorry. I was about to go!
Are you sure you want to do this? You didn't forget it, did you?
I thought homeroom had been prolonged too long, but... I wonder if it's different.
If you have and offer, can I ask you?
Because I wanted to see you soon.
Well, I'm going to pick you up from here.
It's perfect then. I'll go soon.
▲高嶺＊＊▲, you were here. Let's go.
Hey, isn't today your turn? Did you erase the blackboard?
It's fine. When I looked into the classroom, it was clean.
（I didn't erase it... No way, ▲高嶺＊＊▲ did？）
Were you still in the classroom?
Yes, I'm going out now. Sorry.
Hey, it's you turn today, so write in the log and then go home.
I know... Sorry, ▲高嶺＊＊▲. Wait a second.
Hmm. Then, let me see how you work today, okay?
Oh, it's my turn to do class chores. I didn't write in the class log.
I'm already waiting for you, so write quickly.
Well, after all it's good. I'll write tomorrow morning.
Really? Then, let's review today's class so as not to forget, yes.
The first period was... What was it again.
Are you sure you want to do this tomorrow?
Hmm? Oh... A the teacher of life guidance.
... I'm glad. He can't find me.
It's rare to see ▲高嶺＊＊▲ hidding from a teacher.
...Yes. Because that teacher makes fun of me in a loud voide.
Emm... Let's not talk about that.
I was here... What are you talking about?
Ha ha, see you. Have your girlfriend comfort you!
（I should keep quiet about the test）
Oh, it's Tanake's partner. Is it a date?
Yes, special training for doubles... I'm kidding.
If you make Takane cry, we won't forgive you!
I wonder, what are they playing?
（We are..., hidden ▲高嶺＊＊▲ fans... And we are full）
I'm sorry, today is no good.
I see, I understand. Why... only you. You're a fool!
What's with the fighting? What's the cause?
（"▲高嶺＊＊▲". It's hard to say it's you...）
Oh,▲高嶺＊＊▲. What are you doing?
Yes, someone I don't know tells me to give my email address. Of coure... did you know I refused?
（Having a cute girlfried is a lot of work...）
▲高嶺＊＊▲, I came to pick you up.
Thank you. Well then, let's go.
Yeah, I have a dictionary. Today's class changed, so there are only 3 dictionaries.
（You bring your dictionary everyday... As expected of▲高嶺＊＊▲）
Are you okay? I swing my bag so much.
Haha, when I saw▲高嶺＊＊▲ do that, my tension went up.
I see..., but I know you often pass here.
（Everything... I can't do anything wrong now）
Sorry to keep you waiting, let's go.
Oh, I ran in the corridor...
Haha, that's a violation of the school rules.
Does it hurt? If you got hurt, today's date is no good.
It's dangerous if you run in the corridors. I won't go anywhere. Do not run in the corridor, okay?
I feel like I've forgotten something...
Eh, it can't be. Wait for me, I'll get it right away!
▲高嶺＊＊▲! I didn't notice at all.
I'm sorry... I waved my hand, but you didn't notice it.
I wish I could talk to you.
Emm... if I reach this point and call out to you, will I lose? ...I'm kidding.
（... I wonder if ▲高嶺＊＊▲ is making a joke... maybe）
▲主人公＊▲. I'm sorry, the time is...
No, I saw a dog a while ago. I was looking for it.
Can I ask you for a favor?
I'd like you to give this letter to a boy in your class...
Yes, it's from a friend of mine, isn't it? Don't be so surprised, okay?
Excuse me. Is it true that you're dating Takane?
▲主人公＊▲. That girl just now... a firt year? Do you know her?
Oh, you look when you are together like that.
▲主人公＊▲. My teacher asked me is "I was going in a date" now...
▲高嶺＊＊▲. I'm sorry, did you wait much?
No, not at all. Then, let's go.
Oh, today's mixed doubles it's fine. Hahaha.
Hey, what does mixed doubles mean?
Yo, sorry to make you wait.
Go home early, so you don't worry your family.
Alright. Well, if it's Takane I won't worry.
（That phrase to Oyama... You're amazing▲高嶺＊＊▲）
Sorry to keep you waiting... What are you looking for?
Oh,▲高嶺＊＊▲. It looks like I've lost my wallet..., I maybe dropped it...
I got you covered. Your friend asked me to give it to you.
Second year, Takane-san. Head to the staff room...
It's fine, you were called, but why?
A teacher asked me to represent the second years at the school meeting.
So that was it. I thought they were angry at you.
Geez... I haven't done anything wrong.
（▲高嶺＊＊▲ is late...? I wonder if I should send her a mail）
A pity, you found me... I wanted to scare you but... I failed.
I'm glad I send that email.
Ah... over ther, one of my classmates...
Hmm? Oh, I've seen him. Huh, are you dating?
Yes, it's correct... Fufu, it looks like it's fun.
Hmm... did you know? The girls immediately notice your line of sight.
When I'm dating you, I remember when I was little, I used to play date with Papa...
It's nice to have such parent-child date or something. I bet the small ▲高嶺＊＊▲ was cute...
I made a mistake, ▲高嶺＊＊▲ is cute overall!
Don't look at them, it's wrong.
I'm still training. I'm more powerful, right? ...I'm kidding.
（Even if I knew it was a joke, I was scared...）
You threw it into the trash. I knew it,▲高嶺＊＊▲ is great.
Not that. I've read in a book that the city is dirty because people throws more trash than people can pick.
I see, then I should help the people who picks it up.
Oh, there's something on my neck, look at it.
Is that the song I'm humming?
How about it. Absolute pitch, it's interesting.
The man you were talking about... Were you playing a game?
Do you want to do it together? What of games do you like?
Emm... nervous breakdown... speed, that kind of thing?
Huh, did you get the flyers they were giving out?
Sweet potato bread... It looks delicious, isn't it?
It's Mama. It says, "Are you still on a date".
... Fufu. I said "I'm still with him", she said "I don't mind then, enjoy"
...Ah, it looks like a mistake. Sorry, were you surprised?
It's from Mama. I was asked to go shopping.
▲主人公＊▲. Wait, there's lint on your clothes.
Oh, ▲高嶺＊＊▲ you also have some.
I remember the grooming of animals.
No, I don't remember it at all. I set something wrong.
Geez, are you sure you are alright?
Ah... new product release at Winning Burger.
E-mail magazine? I was using it so much before I knew it.
When you register, you will get a great coupon, isn't it amazing?
I have something in my eyes...
Hey, look over there. They're kissing over there.
Then, see you. I hope tomorrow will be like today, and tomorrow and the day after tomorrow.
That's right. Then, see you tomorrow at school.
See you tomorrow. Don't be late.
Well then, see ya. I'll be off tomorrow, but you should do your homework tonight... I'm kidding.
See ya. Don't stay up late because you'll be asleep tomorrow.
Ah,▲高嶺＊＊▲... Hmm,▲高嶺＊＊▲I'll be fine. See ya.
I might be a little tired. I'll have an early start tomorrow and I want to relax. See ya.
